241
00:14:37,000 --> 00:14:39,240
My best friend Arad is now a halfling.

242
00:14:39,240 --> 00:14:40,240
Well, that's me.

243
00:14:40,240 --> 00:14:41,240
He means me.

244
00:14:41,240 --> 00:14:42,240
Oh.

245
00:14:42,240 --> 00:14:47,000
Yes, that's definitely a busy couple of weeks then.

246
00:14:47,000 --> 00:14:48,000
